{"tid":633481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖慎入]法國「三臉」男子成史上首人兩度換臉　醫生：他猶如經歷核戰","createTime":"2018-04-18T10:55:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-20T08:39:36.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"de0ee11d6a07ec7dfa3d9e58bca4a4efae52b5ed","tid":633481,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T10:55:53.000Z","msg":"法國一名男子成史上首個兩度「換臉」的人，被當地傳媒稱作「三臉人」。現年43歲的哈莫（Jerome Hamon）1月完成第二次臉部移植手術後，上周首次離開醫院。他向記者表示感覺良好，指仍然在適應這個「新身份」。<br />\n哈莫因為患有遺傳性疾病「神經纖維瘤症候群」，面部出現腫瘤變形，於是在2010年30多歲時進行第一次臉部移植，包括淚管和眼皮。當時的捐贈者60歲，比哈莫年紀大近一倍。5年後哈莫身體出現排斥現象，直至2017年11月，其臉部組織更開始壞死，負責醫生於是將「舊臉」移除。<br />\n其後哈莫在「無臉」的狀態下生活了兩個月，他形容該段日子猶如「行屍走肉」：「沒有眼皮、耳朵、皮膚等，不能說話及進食。」<br />\n終於到今年1月出現好消息，有第二個人捐出臉部，醫生在手術前花了1個月時間為他全身換血，消除之前治療產生的抗體。<br />\n醫生形容對於一個猶如經歷過核戰的人，哈莫的狀態算是不錯。而這次臉部捐贈者只有22歲，哈莫笑言自己一下子年輕了廿歲。有專家估計類似多次「換臉」的個案會越來越多，因為「慢性排斥（chronic rejection）是事實」，並指雖然不能確定究竟臉部移植可以維持多久，但預計可能與腎臟差不多，一般有10至15年「壽命」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1370966/org/5e5e4b7bd2c9c8a11cf8f0f36f14ffdc.jpg/fMoA7TXvJ8kQx-x04Rzh7DnX0SvzzctCDF_I-gxfyPo?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1370966%2Forg%2F5e5e4b7bd2c9c8a11cf8f0f36f14ffdc.jpg%2FfMoA7TXvJ8kQx-x04Rzh7DnX0SvzzctCDF_I-gxfyPo%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=d553b8a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/179429/%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B-%E4%B8%89%E8%87%89-%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E6%88%90%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A%E9%A6%96%E4%BA%BA%E5%85%A9%E5%BA%A6%E6%8F%9B%E8%87%89-%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F-%E4%BB%96%E7%8C%B6%E5%A6%82%E7%B6%93%E6%AD%B7%E6%A0%B8%E6%88%B0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F179429%2F%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%259C%258B-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E8%2587%2589-%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%258F%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E9%25A6%2596%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E6%258F%259B%25E8%2587%2589-%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%259F-%25E4%25BB%2596%25E7%258C%25B6%25E5%25A6%2582%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E6%25A0%25B8%25E6%2588%25B0&d=HeqzSylQ9iSvFK7c0P5NN%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=ab523ded\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/179429/%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B-%E4%B8%89%E8%87%89-%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E6%88%90%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A%E9%A6%96%E4%BA%BA%E5%85%A9%E5%BA%A6%E6%8F%9B%E8%87%89-%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F-%E4%BB%96%E7%8C%B6%E5%A6%82%E7%B6%93%E6%AD%B7%E6%A0%B8%E6%88%B0</a>"},{"pid":"2f836eb556e6a56a7d54429914c2e6c667624914","tid":633481,"uid":55924,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T10:58:47.000Z","msg":"呢d post 就有圖....."},{"pid":"f339bd1d51717559fb2407952a81c0a8096e6b95","tid":633481,"uid":143289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2f836eb556e6a56a7d54429914c2e6c667624914","tid":633481,"uid":55924,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T10:58:47.000Z","msg":"呢d post 就有圖....."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T10:59:35.000Z","msg":"正正想講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5219427c1a7436f41bafdb5cf9fdf0747a65739b","tid":633481,"uid":61105,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T11:05:43.000Z","msg":"如眼睛可分對或錯"},{"pid":"f730802f3b30163e9d9c626afd74e85d2042dc69","tid":633481,"uid":49697,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T11:11:15.000Z","msg":"大蛇丸咩屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"015ccef9a6ba86a0e2dbd3e1b37155b3b6f6f90b","tid":633481,"uid":55718,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T12:26:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如眼睛可分對或錯</blockquote><br />\n講一講又想睇返套戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54a8b743b9208bac61b5dad5f68e86e37945596f","tid":633481,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T14:15:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":